docs.lead_paragraph: BUENOS AIRES, June 17-- When the fighting broke out between Israel and the Arab countries a wave of near-hysteria crashed through the large Jewish community here. If the Israelis lost, the reasoning went, the so-called Nasserist element in the military Government would gain new heart and frightening strength.
